/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network that powers the city's life. Cars of different colors are scattered along the road, each one a testament to the city's vibrant transportation system. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds, providing a serene backdrop to the busy street below.
